' Basic initialisation 
'Screen Open 1,640,200,16,Hires
Screen Open 1,700,700,18,Hires
Curs Off 
Hide On 
Palette $0,$343,$666,$999,$7B7,$CCC,$9D9,$FEF,$3F3,$FFF,$980,$FF0,$FF9,$F,$6E8,$990,$8AF,$CCC 
Paper 0
Cls 
Ink 2
Text 10,10,"Render code area"
Dim A(10,1)
A(9,1) = 42
If -2 * A(9,1) = (2 * A(9,1)) * (-1)
    Text 10,50,"Hello"
End If
